<h3>About OIC</h3>
<ul>
<li>HQ- Jeddah, Saudi</li>
<li>Official Languages- Arabic, English, French</li>
<li>&nbsp;Has a CHARTER; Signed in 1969</li>
<li>Motto- "to safeguard the interests and ensure the progress and well being of Muslims"</li>
<li>2nd largest Inter governmental organisation after UN</li>
<li>India - 10% of world's Muslims; But still not a part of OIC; Not even Observer Status</li></ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>WHy OIC important for India ?&nbsp;</h3>
<ul>
<li>Natoinal sovereignty&nbsp;</li>
<li>west asia security and peace&nbsp;</li>
<li>Syncretic traditions preserve of islam in India</li></ul>